保罗·梅斯卡尔可能在萨姆·门德斯的新传记片中扮演甲壳虫乐队成员https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mescal-could-be-playing-a-beatle-in-sam-mendes-new-biopic-3759404?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paul-mescal-可能会在萨姆门德斯新传记片中扮演甲壳虫乐队Anagricel DuranFri, 24 May 2024 18:10:48 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3759404 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·梅斯卡尔和披头士乐队。图片来源：Stefania M. D&#39;Alessandro 和 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位奥斯卡提名演员因在 2020 年剧情迷你剧《普通人》中的角色而闻名</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mescal-could-be-playing-a-beatle-in-sam-mendes-new-biopic-3759404">保罗·麦斯卡尔 (Paul Mescal) 可能会在萨姆·门德斯 (Sam Mendes) 的新传记片中扮演甲壳虫乐队成员，这一</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·梅斯卡尔和披头士乐队。图片来源：Stefania M. D&#39;Alessandro 和 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Paul-Mescal-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Stefania-M.-DAlessandro-and-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，萨姆·门德斯可能正在考虑让<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mescal">保罗·梅斯卡尔</a>在他即将上映的<a href="/artists/the-Beatles">披头士</a>传记片中扮演披头士四人组之一。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/all-of-us-strangers-review-paul-mescal-andrew-scott-claire-foy-3576917"><b>《我们都是陌生人》评论：今年最悲伤的电影</b></a></li></ul><p>梅斯卡尔因其在 2020 年电视剧迷你剧《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/normal-people-review-sally-rooney-2651624"><em>普通人》</em></a>中饰演康奈尔·沃尔德伦这一获奖角色而首次受到关注。他还因在 2022 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/aftersun-review-paul-mescal-3351766"><em>《余晖》</em></a>中饰演卡勒姆而获得第 95 届奥斯卡金像奖最佳男主角提名。</p><p>这位演员将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artisits/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特即将上映的</a><i>《角斗士 II》中饰演卢修斯·维鲁斯。</i>维鲁斯是<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator">原版电影</a>反派康茂德（ <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joaquin-phoenix">华金·菲尼克斯饰</a>）的侄子，但从小崇拜已故角斗士马克西姆斯（ <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-crowe">罗素·克劳饰</a>）。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/new-hollywood-a-list-1235905172/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>发布了一个新专题，重点介绍了风靡好莱坞的 10 位年轻电影明星。他们将梅斯卡尔列入名单，并透露即将上映的披头士传记片的导演门德斯希望这位爱尔兰演员能够在影片中扮演利物浦传奇人物之一。 </p><figure id="attachment_3551198" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3551198" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3551198" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new.jpg" alt="保罗·梅斯卡尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paul-Mescal-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3551198" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·梅斯卡尔.图片来源：阿图罗·霍姆斯/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>早在二月份就宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-beatles-announce-details-of-a-biopic-for-each-member-directed-by-sam-mendes-3590045">门德斯将执导四部披头士乐队传记片</a>——一部从乐队成员的角度讲述。</p><p>传记片将从每个乐队成员的角度讲述，并将交叉“讲述历史上最伟大乐队的故事”。</p><p>该项目标志着苹果公司和披头士乐队（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>）以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治·哈里森</a>的家人首次授予一部剧本电影的完整生平故事和音乐版权。</p><p>随着索尼影视娱乐公司将资助和发行这些电影，这些电影将于 2027 年在全球上映，“这些电影的约会节奏，其细节将在临近上映时分享，将是创新和突破性的” – 说乐队在一份声明中。</p><p>这些电影将与门德斯的尼尔街制作公司合作伙伴皮帕·哈里斯和尼尔街的朱莉·帕斯特一起制作。杰夫·琼斯 (Jeff Jones) 将为苹果公司 (Apple Corps Ltd.) 担任执行制片人。</p><p> “我很荣幸能够讲述有史以来最伟大的摇滚乐队的故事，并很高兴能够挑战电影之旅的概念，”门德斯分享道。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonburys-pilton-palais-cinema-announces-2024-line-up-paul-mescal-andrew-scott-florence-pugh-3757874">梅斯卡尔被宣布为今年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节在 Palais 电影院的特邀嘉宾之一，</a>与安德鲁·斯科特和导演安德鲁·黑格一起就他们的情感电影《<i>我们都是陌生人》进行问答。</i></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mescal-could-be-playing-a-beatle-in-sam-mendes-new-biopic-3759404">保罗·梅斯卡尔可能在萨姆·门德斯的新传记片中扮演甲壳虫乐队成员的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
