斯的超级粉丝——她只是个十足的书呆子。她学习成绩最好，她的头脑里有一个令人惊叹的大脑，她的胸膛里有一颗令人惊叹的心脏。我爱 Shura，而且我知道她正在研究新的东西。” </p><figure id="attachment_3757103" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3757103" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3757103" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3757103" class="wp-caption-text"> KT Tunstall 现场表演。图片来源：C Brandon/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>通斯托尔补充道：“我很期待今天的颁奖典礼，因为我肯定会听到一些我从未听说过的艺术家的声音。我非常兴奋，因为他们都在走一条有时非常困难的道路。我钦佩任何这样做的人，所以我迫不及待地想了解他们所做的事情。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-yussef-dayes-and-skepta-and-more-win-at-2024-ivor-novello-awards-3759013">请在此处查看 2024 年 Ivor Novellos 获奖者的完整名单</a>。当晚的其他亮点包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-bruce-springsteens-full-ivors-speech-while-i-was-stone-cold-born-in-the-barrels-of-the-usa-at-16-i-desperately-yearned-to-be-british-3759240">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 荣获艾弗奖学金 (Ivor Fellowship Award)</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-paul-mccartneys-full-roasting-of-bruce-springsteen-from-the-ivors-2024-3759277">保罗·麦卡特尼爵士 (Sir Paul McCartney) 的严厉批评</a>）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-interview-lasso-ivor-novellos-country-reading-leeds-3759161">拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 荣获国际特别奖</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/ne